Page	Route	Key data
Homepage	/	Latest result, standings snapshot, top performers
Standings	/standings	W-L, win%, streak — already has OG image in admin
Games	/games	Full game list, filterable by season/type
Game Detail	/games/:id	Box score, POTG, recap writeup, YouTube embed
Teams	/teams	4 team cards with record
Team Detail	/teams/:id	Roster + team stat averages
Player Profile	/players/:id	Bio, career totals, per-game averages
League Leaders	/leaders	Top 5 per category (PPG, RPG, APG, STL, BLK)


